Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:15.30,OPED,,0,0,0,,尔已开拔\N{\K344\fn DFGMaruGothic-SB\fs39\bord1\c&H0001cd&\3c&Hffffff&\pos(500,1050)}奴らも錨を上げ出す
